ple’s Second Amendment rights.</h2><p class="meta"> <span class="byline author vcard"> <a href="https://reason.com/people/jacob-sullum/" title="Posts by Jacob Sullum" class="author url fn" rel="author">Jacob Sullum</a> </span> <span class="pipe">|</span> <time class="updated" datetime="2020-03-05T08:30:24-05:00">3.5.2020 8:30 AM</time></p><div class="rcom-social-tools"><a href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Freason.com%2F2020%2F03%2F05%2Fshe-said-he-said-he-saw-demons-then-he-had-to-give-up-his-guns%2F" target="_blank" class="rcom-social-tools--button rcom-social--facebook" data-ga-click="true" data-ga-category="Social Share Button Clicked" data-ga-action="Social Share Click - Facebook" data-ga-label="article header"><i class="fab fa-facebook"></i></a><a href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=https%3A%2F%2Freason.com%2F2020%2F03%2F05%2Fshe-said-he-said-he-saw-demons-then-he-had-to-give-up-his-guns%2F&text=A+bizarre+Florida+%E2%80%9Cred+flag%E2%80%9D+case+shows+the+importance+of+safeguards+that+protect+gun+owners+from+unsubstantiated+complaints.&via=reason" target="_blank" class="rcom-social-tools--button rcom-social--twitter" data-ga-click="true" data-ga-category="Social Share Button Clicked" data-ga-action="Social Share Click - Twitter" data-ga-label="article header"><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i></a><a href="https://www.reddit.com/submit?url=https%3A%2F%2Freason.com%2F2020%2F03%2F05%2Fshe-said-he-said-he-saw-demons-then-he-had-to-give-up-his-guns%2F&title=A+bizarre+Florida+%E2%80%9Cred+flag%E2%80%9D+case+shows+the+importance+of+safeguards+that+protect+gun+owners+from+unsubstantiated+complaints." target="_blank" class="rcom-social-tools--button rcom-social--reddit" data-ga-click="true" data-ga-category="Social Share Button Clicked" data-ga-action="Social Share Click - Reddit" data-ga-label="article header"><i class="fab fa-reddit"></i></a><a href="mailto:?subject=Shared+From+Reason.com%3A+A+bizarre+Florida+%E2%80%9Cred+flag%E2%80%9D+